a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">艾拉妮丝·莫里塞特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weezer">威泽</a>（20年来首次在马德里演出）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thirty-seconds-to-mars">火星三十秒</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">圣文森特等人</a>。 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">正义</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">集团党</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">凯撒酋长</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">袋熊</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jet">喷气机、</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glass-animals">玻璃动物</a>等等。</p><p>今年的这一长期举办的音乐节将于 7 月 10 日至 12 日期间举行。活动将返回马德里 Villaverde 场地， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mad-cool-announces-festival-site-improvements-for-2024-3597566">音乐节组织者宣布今年该音乐节进行了一系列改进，</a>包括减少舞台数量，以及公共容量的普遍减少，以减少日程冲突和艺术家重叠。</p><p>您可以<a href="https://www.madcooltickets.com/en-index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到门票，并查看下面的完整阵容和日期划分。 </p><figure id="attachment_3831139" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831139" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831139" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Mad Cool 2025 天分裂海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2499" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Mad-Cool-2025-day-splits-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1739.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/