蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet) 表示，他将《沙丘第二部分》爆米花桶放在床底下https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-says-he-keeps-his-dune-part-two-popcorn-bucket-under-his-bed-3831118?ut m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = timothee-chalamet-说他将他的沙丘第二部分爆米花桶放在他的床下Victoria LuxfordWed, 22 Jan 2025 15:40:54 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3831118 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他将病毒式传播的物品描述为“一件明确的事情”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/timothee-chalamet-says-he-keeps-his-dune-part-two-popcorn-bucket-under-his-bed-3831118">蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet) 称他将“沙丘第二部分”爆米花桶放在床底下，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="蒂莫西·柴勒梅德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Timothee-Chalamet-premiere-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·柴勒梅德 (Timothée Chalamet)</a>谈到了去年大片<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune-part-two"><em>《沙丘：第二部分》</em></a>中爆米花桶的风靡一时，并透露他在床下放了一个爆米花桶。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/timothee-chalamet-bob-dylan-musical-performances-a-complete-unknown-3829205">蒂莫西·查拉梅在《完全未知》中的最佳音乐表演</a></strong></li></ul><p>在社交媒体帐户<em>Triple_j 发布的一次采访中，</em>柴勒梅德在宣传他的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-dylan">《鲍勃·迪伦</a>传记片<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/a-complete-unknown">《完全未知》</a> 》时，向查拉梅展示了促销爆米花桶，其盖子形状像沙虫。</em></p><p>联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elle-fanning">艾丽·范宁</a>对查拉梅说：“你告诉我你有其中一个，对吗？”他回答说：“是的，我把我的放在床底下”，并补充道：“他们会模糊这一点当你把它拉起来时，这就像一个明确的事情”，开玩笑地暗示网上评论说爆米花桶看起来很粗鲁。</p><p>采访最后提出了一个关于<em>《完全未知》</em>的促销爆米花桶是什么样子的问题。 “那是吉他孔”演员笑着回答。</p><p>去年，《<em>沙丘：第二部分》</em>促销爆米花桶 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-dune-popcorn-bucket-why-is-it-going-viral-3598081">在网上引起了广泛的反响</a>，从笑话到彻底的厌恶。虽然促销爆米花桶并不是什么新鲜事，但人们对此的反应意味着其他电影也发布了类似的搭配，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/deadpool-and-wolverine"><em>《死侍与金刚狼》</em></a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/deadpool-wolverine-popcorn-bucket-goes-viral-dune-popcorn-bucket-all-over-again-3778752">暗示性设计</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFCa8mXp_bX/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style=